      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. The suspension geometry remains tight, offering exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. Recent service includes a VANOS system inspection and subframe reinforcement, addressing key platform vitals. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp, making this a visceral choice for the purist enthusiast.",
